Package gov.nasa.jpl.constraint

package gov.nasa.jpl.constraint
Package that contains the Constraint interface and all its subclasses. These provide passive constraint checking as one models, but cannot be used for scheduling. For active constraints, see 'Condition' in the scheduler package
